[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]9月1日凌晨0点，“内布拉斯加号”（{{lang|en|State of Nebraska}}）汽船在[[百慕大|百慕大]]和加拿大[[塞布尔岛_(加拿大)|塞布尔岛]]之间的中途海域附近发现本季首场风暴，起初测得每小时130公里的[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]，相当于现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的一级飓风强度。{{#tag:ref|[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]于1971年面世<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | author = Jack Williams | title = Hurricane scale invented to communicate storm danger | publisher = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2005-05-17 | accessdate = 2013-08-04 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324154907/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-24 }}</ref>，再对[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]大西洋飓风数据库的所有风暴追溯分级<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | title = Chronological List of All Continental United States Hurricanes: 1851-2012 | date = 2013-06 | accessdate = 2016-11-10 | archivedate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503012801/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。|group="注"}}<ref name="HURDAT" />9月1日晚，“恩格尔伯特号”（{{lang|en|Engelbert}}）[[三桅帆船|三桅帆船]]的桅杆横梁在飓风中失落，被迫改道向塞布尔岛以东洋面行驶。此外，还有“纳夫帕克托斯号”（{{lang|en|Naupactus}}）船只遭遇大浪，装载的部分货物落水。<ref name="1996a">{{cite report | author1 = Jose F. Partagas | author2 = Henry F. Diaz | date = 1996 | title = Year 1884 | accessdate = 2016-12-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304093331/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/1884-1886/1884.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/1884-1886/1884.pdf | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | format = PDF }}</ref>9月2日清晨，气旋减弱成热带风暴，之后不久就从[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]东南部登陆。风暴加速向东北移动，于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}9月3日凌晨0点左右在[[圣约翰斯_(纽芬兰-拉布拉多)|圣约翰斯]]东北方向约740公里海域转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。温带残留向[[罗盘方位|东北偏东]]移动，经过大西洋并袭击[[爱尔兰岛|爱尔兰岛]]，最终于9月6日晚逐渐消散。<ref name="HURDAT" />飓风季过后的一个多世纪里，这场风暴都没有加入大西洋飓风数据库，直到1996年再根据[[气象学|气象学家]]何塞·费尔南德斯-帕塔加斯（{{lang|en|Jose Fernandez-Partagas}}）和亨利·迪亚兹（{{lang|en|Henry Diaz}}）的研究结果列入<ref name="1996a" /><ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] }}</ref>。
